snippet.title: RDCworld1 on Meeting Lebron James & the SECRET to Viral Videos
snippet.description:
On this episode of The CouRage and Nadeshot Show podcast, RDCworld1 members Mark Phillips, Ben, and Dylan come onto the show as guests and break down how they met on Xbox Live, meeting Lebron James and J. Cole, how they create their viral sketches, favorite anime, and more! 

Subscribe — https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnrX2_FoKieobtw19PiphDw?sub_confirmation=1

48:16 - Best at games
